Hello,

For your convenience, we would like to schedule a virtual HCV orientation w=
ith your household on Thursday, March 19th. The two time slots available ar=
e 10am-11am or 11am-12pm. Once we know your preference for time, we will el=
ectronically send you the packet of information that we will review during =
the orientation, and a zoom link.

Thank you,

Kati

